Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The history of games can be traced back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the way to Ancient Egypt 5,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These ancient games decided the fate of the citizens and the kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They were called the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the time where a boy has solved the Millennium Puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and released the Dark Games has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A boy with both a heart of light and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People refer to him as Yuugiou: The Game King.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lost Exodia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus has the power to read his opponent's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really beat an opponent who can read my entire hand and strategies?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of me, Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get back the person important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother Katsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made this video so you won't forget my face, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SHIZUKA!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, I won't be able to see your face anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I didn't really want to talk through a video.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:03:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But face-to-face...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see your face one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Last time"...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, bye bye, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An invitation for entering the Kingdom...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go by boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means the battlefield for this tournament is on an island, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says at 10:30 P.M. I should board from Domino Pier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An invitation to the Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, is your grandfather there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no choice but to go to that island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this sure was surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:04:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe your grandfather was taken just like that while we were out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man, Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, we can't get aboard the ship without an invitation card...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find a way to go there with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be great if we could all go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this "Glory of the King's Hand" card...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge cash-prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cash prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means the winner will receive a huge cash prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let me see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge cash prize...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you can see the sunset crystal clear from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, your grandfather taught me the heart of the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thankful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And get gramps back here safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad to have met someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you say such a random thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, I was ready to finish the Millennium Puzzle given to me by Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that this puzzle was found in Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't completed it yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I really don't know what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, It's something that can be seen, but is not seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wished a lot on the puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling that the Millennium Puzzle would grant this wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I met you and Honda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you can call that a "meeting".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I always got pissed off whenever I looked at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying this is your treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then a senior who was pretending to be my bodyguard,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ushio-senpai, showed his true objection was my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Yugi,\N you still owe me some money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bodyguard fee... ¥200,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good chance to pay them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should beat these guys up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'll do that to my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange guy you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about you{\i1} as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time, I told my wishes to the Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to get some friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you got the final piece of the Puzzle for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to learn from you, and now have my own treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, my treasure is something that you can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but {\i1}can't{\i0} see at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and you know what the treasure is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't see{\i1} friendship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I really say something that corny?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be best if we could all go together...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hearts will always be with you, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Just put your heart into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chosen Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the event held by Industrial Illusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:08:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have investigated every single one of your Duel Monsters records.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are all excellent Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you each have an equal chance of winning this tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, all your heads...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are surrounded by a bright halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, all my fellow Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go across the ocean, to get your greatest honor in the Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please show your Star Chips when boarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your Star Chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, chill out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take this kid out of here. Go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hands off! I know the Yugi Mutou who beat Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be crazy! I'll throw you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's interesting! If you think you can beat me, I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun... Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I was worried about you going by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let my friend aboard the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no exception!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those with a Star Chip can board the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun {\i1}has{\i0} a Star Chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card says anyone with a Star is a Duelist eligible to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the other Duelists all have 2 Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Even by being at a disadvantage...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would choose to be with Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, it's me. The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't get so close to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that you came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That crappy Pegasus stole something you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I'll never forget your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that boy, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! What a nice woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really unexpected that a shrimp like you beat Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're famous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, I'm a friend of the famous Duelist Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a great Duelist, ya know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:11:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a Duel, even if the opponent is a shrimp, I won't go easy on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel me~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Mai Kujaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you around, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two sex maniacs worry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how men are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They let us on a giant ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's only one big shared room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there any single rooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why are ya talkin' so loud in da lounge?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yugi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you Yugi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insector Haga and Dinosaur Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, only champions like us get da single rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haga-kun! Congratulations to you for winning the championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I was holdin' back 'gainst this loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna be the winners in this tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:12:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, even though I was the champion last week...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel very successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't until I beat champions like you or Kaiba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we will Duel at the Kingdom, Yugi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same here, so please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Ain't he jus' a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Do you know the new rules of the Duels?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard you should think of new strategies aside from your normal ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, for me, it don't really matter if der's rules 'er not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just beat da crap outta each otha'. Dat's da only rule fer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, you're really good. I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna rest in my single room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}don't{\i0} like him... The bastard pisses me off...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room isn't any worse than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look around, they're beginning to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People can trade cards from their card collections...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To improve their Decks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, they get the advantage of learning about their opponents before the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Insector Haga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see those cards? They look strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These people can't be trusted with cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want a lady like me to stay in a room without even a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... those are the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask the person responsible to get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actin' like dis is gonna get yer ass thrown off da ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do ya wanna sleep in {\i1}my{\i0} room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'm happy! {\i1}Really{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fer real!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't stand it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! I'm not a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that Bakura-kun just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's Bakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd ya think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This's da "Special Guest" room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki-san, you must be {\i1}so{\i0} good at cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}love{\i0} to challenge strong men.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who d'ya think yer talkin' ta here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for ya ta beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do you wanna have a Duel with me right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd ya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you win, I'll do {\i1}anything{\i0} you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got some new cards from trading.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me! Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H0FC118&\1a&H00&}Salamandra{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFF00FF&\1a&H00&}Chain-Equipped Boomerang{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunai With Chain
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H57D8E4&\1a&H00&}Baby Dragon{\r} and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H0FC118&\1a&H00&}Shield in the Right Hand, Sword in the Left Hand{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With these Magic Cards, you'll get a way more powerful strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this tournament is not as easy as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, use this one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H000000&\1a&H00&\frz120\pos(118,627)\bord0\shad0}Time Wizard
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll give you a hand when you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yugi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haga-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, shuffle the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}so{\i0} lucky tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will guess those cards with my eyes shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Dat's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first card is {\1c&H0FC118&\1a&H00&}Shadow of Temptation{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second card is {\1c&H71C1C7&\1a&H00&}Harpie Lady{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is {\1c&H0FC118&\1a&H00&}Kaleidoscope{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth is {\1c&H0FC118&\1a&H00&}Cyber Bondage{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Unreal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my card trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any given time, I know the next card I will draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's play the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose, you must leave the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya really want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you trade cards with anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm using my own cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your Deck, you have the one card that beat Kaiba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H0856C0&\1a&H00&}Exodia{\r}, was it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have a look at that legendary card?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's been found out,\N there's no point in hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, you know my strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So this is {\1c&H0856C0&\1a&H00&}Exodia the Sealed One{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(680,705)}Exodia the Forbidden One
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:17:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-kun, I've been thinking of a way to beat this card for a long time now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't come up with anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I finally found a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be over for sure if I do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I have no more opponents!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The treasured cards my grandpa gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get aboard quickly, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Living is more important than those cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some things in this world that need to be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some things that can't be replaced!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some things just cannot be lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found the second one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, just three more to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just three left...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya weaklin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help, but why did you come on the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't want to leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only found two cards for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "okay"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help {\i1}anyone{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my own little sister, Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a little sister, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents got divorced when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's very far away now, living with my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my sister was born, she had bad eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, she will go blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last week, she sent me a video tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see your face one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess her doctor warned her that the time she'd been dreading is coming near.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This problem's not easy to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some experienced doctors with good needed equipment in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to see one of the doctors, but I don't have enough money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to win this tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm the winner, I'll get the cash prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have a chance of saving Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun, we will make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me for my grandpa, and you for your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, be confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, land!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insector Haga, I will beat you in this Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, we arrived at Pegasus's Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During these two days, only those who collect 10 Star Chips can enter the Finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Yugi, first go beat the shameless Insector Haga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Invited to the forest, a Duel Ring suddenly appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Haga laughing?
